struct Point
    number x
    number y
end struct

variable d is empty dictionary from struct Point to string
change value of make Point with x 0, y 0 in d to "origin"
change value of make Point with x 1, y 2 in d to "p12"
say d contains make Point with x 0, y 0
say d contains make Point with x 9, y 9
say value of make Point with x 1, y 2 in d
say length of d
